<br>
Chanters are useless on many raids.  Anyone who has never heard a chanter complain about that has probably not been playing long, or seen a chanter quit to start a twink after agonizing endlessly about it.<br>
<br>
Warriors have VERY low damage output.  They're great at what they do, but if you're going to do a raid with only cleric/warrior/chanter, it will be a raid that will truly suck, and probably be in danger because of low damage output, to say the least.  Cler/war/chanter only has warrior for significant damage output, and warriors are crappy at melee compared to some of the other classes.  Add chanter mob charms in if you must, but that's stretching the point quite a bit, to little avail.  NOBODY would ever want to be stuck in the utter misery of a cleric/war/chanter only raid, and it's very far from a guaranteed success.<br>
<br>
The only class that comes even close to a &quot;must have&quot; across the broadest spectrum of raid sizes and types is cleric.<br>
<br>
Everybody else can stand in line.<br>
